contents.shortDescription: The nordic style arrangement features modern and sleek furniture that brightens up and accents your home's living room.
contents.longDescription: Modernize your living room by using the nordic style arrangement. Nordic style elements include furniture and lighting that contain cool tones and open designs that are sure to inspire every homeowner.
contents.name: Nordic Style

sKUs.shortDescription: A simple and modern casual sofa that offers comfort and contemporary styling to accent your home's living room.
sKUs.longDescription: Give your living room an open and modern feel with the Nordic single sofa. The sofa features a modern simple design, wide armrests, layered cushioning, and easy to clean polyester fabric. The sofa's modern styling is complemented with wide brushed steel legs. No assembly required.
sKUs.name: Nordic Sofa
